Matrices and Basic Operations

---

EX 1

Question:
For the matrices
A = [ [1, 2],
[3, 4] ]

B = [ [5, 6],
[7, 8] ]

Calculate A + B, AB and A transpose.

Solution:

A + B =
[ [6, 8],
[10, 12] ]

AB =
[ [19, 22],
[43, 50] ]

A transpose =
[ [1, 3],
[2, 4] ]

